dcterms:description: The BACE dataset provides 1547 experimental binary inhibition labels with the 3D positioned ligands aligned to the binding pocket of human β-secretase 1 (BACE-1). It includes 1478 ligands (653 active and 825 inactive) after filtering out large ligands that contained more than 200 heavy atoms.
dcterms:title: BACE dataset

dcterms:creator: J. S. Delaney
dcterms:description: The ESOL dataset contains 1128 aqueous solubility values in log(mol·L-1) with SMILES-encoded molecules, used for regression tasks in predicting molecular properties.
dcterms:title: ESOL dataset
